wsdl:operation.name: CreateHelpDeskTicket
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Create a Help Desk Ticket w/up to 1 attachment. Returns either an HD Case ID # or an error message. All errors begin with 'ERROR:'

wsdl:operation.name: CreateHelpDeskTicketBasic
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Create a Help Desk Ticket w/no attachments. Returns either an HD Case ID # or an error message. All errors begin with 'ERROR:'

wsdl:operation.name: CreateChangeRequestBasic
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Create a ChangeRequest w/no attachments. Returns either an Change ID # or an error message. All errors begin with 'ERROR:'

wsdl:operation.name: CreateChangeRequestNeXpose
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Create a ChangeRequest for NeXpose w/no attachments. Returns either an Change ID # or an error message. All errors begin with 'ERROR:'

wsdl:operation.name: HelpDeskTicketIsOpen
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Checks the status of a Help Desk Ticket. Returns True if open and False if Resolved or Closed.

wsdl:operation.name: GetAMSComputerSystemDataByAssetID
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Returns and ArrayList of ComputerSystem and Associated user Infomation. As there may be more than one user per asset the length of the ArrayList will vary and A UserCount Attribute is returned. All Errors begin with 'ERROR:'
